<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="19Jun1919"><font color="red">19 June 1919</font>, <cite>Letters I</cite> (JJ to Ben Huebsch): Colum &hellip; raised a subsidy of $2000 &hellip; It would greatly facilitate to have this money cabled as we have now reached the crisis.</div>
